i	/	tilde.team	70
i## Conclusion	/	tilde.team	70
i	/	tilde.team	70
iI can now play Sudoku on my UNIX system. I'm really enjoying	/	tilde.team	70
ithe 9ports project, and I'm thinking of porting other	/	tilde.team	70
iapplications, like those on the Plan 9 forks, such as	/	tilde.team	70
